  },
  "concepts": [
    "Estar is always used for location (with few exceptions)",
    "Ser for descriptions of inherent qualities",
    "Estar for conditions that can change",
    "Same adjective can change meaning: ser listo (to be clever) vs estar listo (to be ready)",
    "More prepositions of location: en, cerca de, lejos de, al lado de"
  ],
